data.description: Come put your personal touches on this well maintained 3 bed, 2 bath CONCRETE BLOCK home in a desired location of NW Palm Bay. This home is on CITY WATER.  Master has large ensuite bathroom with jetted tub and separate shower! Large driveway and 2 car garage for plenty of parking. Large enclosed sunroom on the back allows for extra entertainment space and added SF!! Large yard great for a family! Roof is 2013 AC is 2014 water heater is newer as well! Close to everything!  Good bones, well maintained, very clean home that just needs cosmetic updates. Schedule your showing today to see all the potential it has to offer!
